{"comments":[], "Body":"<p>See the approach of <a href=\"http://lingo.stanford.edu/pubs/WP-2001-03.pdf\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sag et al (2001)</a> on multi-word expressions, specifically the parts about light-verb constructions, which they model computationally with an HPSG-based grammar. See references in that paper for background, and also <a href=\"http://www.cl.cam.ac.uk/~aac10/papers/lrec2000.pdf\" rel=\"nofollow\">Copestake &amp; Flickinger (2000)</a>.</p>\n", "Id":"2273", "ParentId":"2271", "CreationDate":"2012-07-19T12:41:05.463", "Score":"1", "PostTypeId":"2", "OwnerUserId":"483", "LastActivityDate":"2012-07-19T12:41:05.463", "OwnerUser":{"UpVotes":"180", "WebsiteUrl":"http://www.buffalo.edu/~lovegren", "Location":"Buffalo, NY", "Id":"483", "DownVotes":"5", "AccountId":"1021213", "Views":"70", "Reputation":"6503", "CreationDate":"2011-11-05T19:57:14.530", "DisplayName":"jlovegren", "LastAccessDate":"2014-01-16T02:42:41.207", "AboutMe":""}}